{"title":"Sim Works: To Smile Bar Dirt Drop Now Comes in a 31.8 Clamp","link":"https://theradavist.com/sim-works-to-smile-bar-dirt-drop-now-comes-in-a-31-8-clamp/","date":1706539719000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/15SImWorks-Tosmilebar7.jpg?fit=1200,1000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/15SImWorks-Tosmilebar7.jpg?w=1500&amp;quality=75 1500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/15SImWorks-Tosmilebar7.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/15SImWorks-Tosmilebar7.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w\" /></p>\n<p><em>Sim Works’ trusty, Nitto-made dirt drop, the <a href=\"https://www.sim.works/products/to-smile\" target=\"_blank\">To Smile</a> bar, is back in stock, and this round, it’s been updated with a 31.8 ⌀ clamp.</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/SIMWORKS_TOSMILE26-1600x1067-1.jpg?fit=1200,1067&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/SIMWORKS_TOSMILE26-1600x1067-1.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/SIMWORKS_TOSMILE26-1600x1067-1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/SIMWORKS_TOSMILE26-1600x1067-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/SIMWORKS_TOSMILE26-1600x1067-1.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/SIMWORKS_TOSMILE37-1600x1067-1.jpg?fit=1200,1067&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/SIMWORKS_TOSMILE37-1600x1067-1.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/SIMWORKS_TOSMILE37-1600x1067-1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, h